{"type": "article", "id": 10506, "title": "Hideaway 儿童椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-08T07:06:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235717aSZWHdEzQ3Vvjbsr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t最近，来自奥克兰的设计工作室 Think &amp; Shift 受新西兰儿童保育公司 New Shoots 之邀，为其设计了一款名为「Hideaway 」的椅子，希望孩子们能远离周遭吵闹的环境，创造一个独处或是玩耍的小空间。Hideaway 是用成型的胶合板鱼软垫组合而成，球形的外壳是由 4 个半圆的胶合板组织在一起的，椅面低至靠近地面的部分也充分考虑到了小孩适用的高度，令小孩们坐在里面感到放松与舒适。软垫是用夹子固定在胶合板上，方便拆卸与清洗。用 Think &amp; Shift 的话说，这是一个令他们重新思考人体工程学与舒适度的产品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235714BKOdeDYPLGXywhs6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235714qGapfW62sx9A0YlT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235715l6dORo8eaqAuQyCS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235715MrYGAlV31fyWnFkm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235716uOoYLSNdTlr6zv0P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}